### Loc for the pneumatic cannon.

pneumatic-cannon-component-itemslot-name = 气罐

## Shown when trying to fire, but no gas

pneumatic-cannon-component-fire-no-gas = { CAPITALIZE(THE($cannon)) }发出咔哒声，但没有气体喷出。

## Shown when changing power.

pneumatic-cannon-component-change-power = { $power ->
    [High] 你将限制器调到了最大功率。感觉有点太强了……
    [Medium] 你将限制器调到了中等功率。
    *[Low] 你将限制器调到了低功率。
}

## Shown when being stunned by having the power too high.

pneumatic-cannon-component-power-stun = { THE($cannon) }的强大冲击力将你击倒！
